content.detailedDescription: Ok so my story starts like this. on 4th on july 2012 or 2013 i cant really remember the year but i know it was 4th of july because i went with my friends to see some firework in a nearby town call denville. its was around i say 10:00pm or later and my friend just dropped me off by my house across the street and right as i shut the door my friend drives off and i live on a busy street so i look both ways and i look left then right and as i look right i see something red circle and not like red blinking light on a plane like a solid red circle and im thinking to myself maybe a firework but usually after like two seconds the firework would go out so now im wtf is this! so instead of crossing the street i stand there watching this red orb coming from the east heading west making no sound at all. i'm thinking to myself what the hell can fly and just be one big red ball.But now hear comes the crazy part! the moon was big that night also so as im watching it going from east to west the red orb goes in front on the moon then the color red goes away and i can see some sort of craft! now im kinda nervous because how in the hell does a red orb ball thing that wasn't blinking flashing making no sound what so ever go in front of the moon and lost the red color! and i can draw this disc craft! and as it keeps going and finally not in front of the moon anymore it turn into a red orb again! then i kept watching it for as long as i can and this lasted for about 13 to 15 minutes. the red orb wasn't going crazy up and down it just kept going steady straight across. it was heading down route 46 west towards the town i came from that i watch the fireworks. i didn't tell anyone and i've felt weird after this event. so give it about a month later i couldn't get this out of my head and i was thinking their has to be someone else out there that saw what i saw!  i cant just be seeing stuff! so i started to googled orbs sighting or ufo sighting over wharton or morris county new jersey...And after about a hour looking through websites i found someone posted about seeing a solid red orb over denville new jersey same date.  i was so happy i found something or someone that saw that same thing! and my story makes sense with the other person story!  the red orb was heading towards denville. but now i cant find that website and i've been looking for those people. i want to talk to them and talk about what we saw. its like im in my own world and i dont want to tell anyone because i dont want to sound crazy!
content.summary: Red orb heading east down route 46 new jersey wharton heading west down route 46

content.detailedDescription: While visiting a local pet store several cars off the side of the street 3 cars with occupants out looking in the sky, so i pulled off to see what they were looking at and there was a silver sphere hovering. as an army veteran that has been deployed to a combat zone i can safely say that this was no publicly aknowledged military aircraft. i moved to take a picture of it with my phone but my phone was glitching like it had a virus or something. the other witnesses said the same was happening with their phones. after joking with them about no believing us without proof some of them started getting in their cars and one of them called out to us saying the radio stations weren't working. the rest of us tried our car stereos a range into nothing but white noise static. we then returned our attention to the object, which appeared to be moving closer, moving smoother that any aircraft i have seen or heard of, and it was moving into the wind. then, if it wasn't strange enough, it just vanished. no flash of light or streaking off somewhere,  it just wasn't there anymore. our phones and radios suddenly went back to normal. this sighting has bothered me for 3 years now. i wanted to at least tell someone.
content.summary: While visiting a local pet store several cars off the side of the street 3 cars with occupants out looking in the sky is pulled off to see what they were looking at and there was a silver orb hovering. never seen a sphere aircraft. then it vanished.

content.detailedDescription:
To whom it may concern,

     i was outdoors at 10:20pm est / essex county, massachusetts. an unidentified flying object appeared from the se traveling nne at tremendous speed. object closely resembled transit of iss/satellite, however it was rapidly ascending during its flyby until almost unobservable. there were no aircraft, satellites or iss in the vicinity during it's passage. the object left no contrail and was devoid of any audible frequency. temperature was 73 degrees f. humidity of 46%, & wind was w @ 7 mph. visibility listed at 9.0 mi. no cloud cover. 

i have a background in aeronautical engineering so please bear with me. human made satellites typically orbit +/- 400 miles in elevation. the speed of these objects can vary due to a number of reasons based on gravity, orbital radius, etc. many satellites travel exceeding 16,000 mph. the iss travels slightly faster, about 17,000 mph. this object was exceeding that speed and increased in altitude beyond the thermosphere @ 419 mi. i cannot estimate the speed of the craft as there are too many unknown variables to be taken into account. 

the object's trajectory and inertial path appeared uninterrupted, ascending in a straightforward motion. the light source was constant yet dimmed as it elevated to a higher position. the time elapsed from my vantage point was between 5-6 seconds (which means nothing in relative terms because the angular diameter and relative scale were also incalculable based on other unknowns). 

for the record of this report, i would like to express my certainty regarding the validity of this sighting based on my personal experience/expertise in this field. also, i have never filed a report before, even though this is far from the most unusual thing i have ever observed. unfortunately, the two perticular incidents i am referring to aside from this one, are far more complex and compelling. it would require substantial dialogue in order to accurately illustrate and covey the intricacies of those sightings. 

i hope there are others out there who had an opportunity to observe this anomaly and perhaps we can accurately determine its destination/point of origin/and or other possibilities that i cannot think of. 

thank you (mufon) for your service to those ladies and gentlemen out there who have a realistic understanding of what is potentially out 'there'. 

best regards
content.summary: Unidentified flying object appeared from se traveling n at tremendous speed. no satellites/iss or aircraft present during flyby.

content.detailedDescription: Me my husband and daughter were outside enjoying a summer day with grand kids and i looked up above the trees was a super bright glowing object in the sky no noise came from it and i told them too look up its a ufo and my daughter kept saying its a plain that the sun was reflecting on but it wasn't it made no noise plains here are loud especially that close  ...I took out my phone and took a few pics.It moved very slowly across the sky .
content.summary: Saw in afternoon outside

content.detailedDescription: I soo wanted to share an experience both my husband and i have had. we were coming home after a truck pulling contest about 1:30am on hwy 20 heading west, going 60mph when i saw a blue pepsi can color light that morphed right before us and stayed with our speed for about 2-3 minutes or more! it was hovering just above the corn tops just on the other side of the road. i suppose they were checking us out so to speak. the front of the small ship was blinking a bright white, and the rest of the ship was that pepsi blue color. after we both were checking each other out, the ship slowly and carefully lowered a deer that to me seemed to be the size of a fawn with folded legs down to the ground where the deer now full sized ran across the road in front of us. i looked out the back of the truck window and the ship had gone back to the size of a small blue star or light and went on its way continuing along the tops of the corn. since this incident, we have seen them several times and the last time the body of the small ship it was the same size, but had the blue outline and we could almost see thru it. it was once again close to the road not caring that we saw it. the other blue lights were in a field going up and down as if they were working. neither of us will forget it. i had a camera with me but was afraid to use it and sooo wish i would have taken a picture of it. we have binos, and camera and cameras on our phones now so we are ready to see more!We also have drawings in our files of various ones that we have seen since!
content.summary: Began as a blue light size of a blue reflector and changed to oval shaped ship. gently laid a deer with folded legs onto the ground

content.detailedDescription: My son was running behind our house at sunset in a wooded area, beneath power lines on 25 may 2016. at 20:55 he saw an orange globe-shaped object silently hovering in place in the western sky. he ran toward it to get closer, stopped and took two pictures. two beams of light appeared below the craft, but did not reach the ground. the beams appeared to be part of the propulsion system as moments after the beams appeared, the object slowly moved to the east. the beams did not point straight down, instead were slightly angled outward. he lost view of the object as it slowly moved behind the trees to the east. he texted me to come see an odd object in the sky, i ran out there, but it had disappeared behind the trees at that point. we ran down the hill to see if we could see it, but it was gone.
content.summary: Orange globe hovering silently, then two beams of light came from the bottom of craft and it slowly moved to the east.

content.detailedDescription: May 24th 2016, 9:15pm norfolk virginia. i was looking at stars and thought this was just another satellite until i noticed a grey rectangle bar close behind it giving it a triangular shape. directly behind that, very close, was a plane? with white blinking lights. for a second it looked like one long object. white blinking object started going to the right of smaller front object, now they were side by side. front object started to go left creating a larger gap between the 2. blinking plane? headed left(as if following) and moved to the left side of smaller front object, now side by side again. last i saw (trees were about to block view) front object was going right again creating more space between it and blinking object on its left. i've watched the skies for 30 years hoping to see something ~out of the ordinary~ and last night was it! :-) total time 2 minutes.
content.summary: Thought was satelite then noticed grey rectangle shaped bar which gave triangular appearance to front light followed closely by plane? white blinking lights

content.detailedDescription:
My 31 year old son and i went out on our deck last night 05/24/2016 and immediately i noticed an amber ball of light streaking in from the west. it then stopped abruptly and hovered. i quickly took a picture.  it then started slowly moving east (over a 2 hour period) after it cleared the western trees we could start to see the shear mass of it.  there were 3 white lights way below it that were moving with it.  as the moon brightened we could see the shap of a triangle that connected all of the lights..  it was like a mountain moving through the sky it was so big.  we watched it for 2 hours or so until it left the clearing.  i will chalk this up as one of the most unexplainable things i have ever seen in my life.

the videos do not do it justice, it does not pick up the bottom 3 lights that connect it all and the 3rd light was not visible to us until later.   but that's ok, it was amazing.
content.summary: Massive mountain like triangle slowly moved through the sky over a 2 hour period

content.detailedDescription:
This is the second vaguely similar object i've seen in my life, both viewed from cheltenham uk. the first i reported on here a few years ago, which was a white/yellow light which moved location three times over the course of a minute then from still shot off and away in a curved tick in about a quarter of a second. i was the only witness. that anomaly is ingrained in my mind, happened 10pmish march 2010 over lilleybrook golf course.

the second unexplainable object i have seen in my life (the one i am reporting now in this case) happened a couple of years later, i think around late february 2012, to which there were two witnesses. 

nearing dusk, around 5pm my friend and i decided to drive up the local hill in cheltenham (leckhampton hill, 900ft) and go for a walk up there. we parked the car in the carpark, walked up the hill through the woods until we came out near the top at a clearing, which overlooks the town of cheltenham with a clear view for about 40 miles around, west, north and north east. the town was down below us and it was a crisp pale blue/white sky, fading into dusk. the town lies 1000ft below and infront of us, street lights starting to come on, and then for the next 30 miles north it is relatively flat until you reach the malvern hills, worcestershire. 

we were looking out to the horizon and admiring the malvern hill range, as they stick out of nowhere in the southern english countryside. there was still light in the sky but darkening, i suddenly saw a white light 'turn on' in the sky, slightly above and to the right of the end of the malvern hill range. i said to my friend, "oh look a plane's turned it's lights on"...(not sure if they ever actually do do that!).....We carried on talking for another 20 seconds or so when we both noticed the light had now moved above the malvern hills and was doing various looping patterns in the sky above the hill range. the motions it made were like figures of eight and circling loops, up and down and side to side, whilst smoothly accelerating and deccelerating. all very smooth motions, changing direction, speeding up and slowing down. this lasted for about 30 seconds and during this time it changed colour, fading from it's initial white, to and intense gold, then yellow and then just firey orange, the same colour as a standard street light in the uk.     

now having turned to orange it dropped down below the top of the malvern hills, and was bright orange infront of the black (rather dusky now) hill range. it slowly and steadily decsended down, and in a straight line moved at a seemilngly constant rate accross the dark countryside in the direction of gloucester. (so from our pov the malrverns were infront of us, and the object moved down diagonally left [west])

we finally lost sight of it when it reached the city of gloucester and as it had appeared to be near ground level since it left the malverns it just merged into the city lights. the whole sighting lasted about a minute and a half, during which my friend and i both kept saying "what the hell isss that??!!" we both recounted what we saw to each other afterwards, and both agreed that the object had traveled from the malvern hills to gloucester (around 23 miles) in around 30 seconds. i did try to film it initially but quickly realised that the phone i had at the time the camera app was not working properly. very annoying! (not sure how good the quality would have been anyway!)


there are often strange objects that cannot be identified in the night sky, but until they do something distinctly bizzarre, i usually tend to write them off... hope to see another one one day, i'm only 31 and am looking up more than ever now! :d



ps i have included a .Jpg of the view we had at the time (we were slightly higher up, and it was a bit darker), the white dot is about the same size and location as where the object first 'turned on'... we then noticed it again a very short while later and it had then moved to the left and proceeded to loop and fade colour, very rough patterning done in microsoft paint. sorry for the crudeness!

i hope this report helps fit another small peice to the seemingly infinitely large puzzle!
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: White light 'turned on' in sky, then looped randomly and faded colours to gold and firey orange, then traveled 20 miles in 40 seconds and merged into city lights

Warning bad english !!

2 day before weekend on 20 may 2016,i was meditating around 8.30 pm in my room like my everyday routine after my son sleep. while meditating about half an hour,and do some random telepathy to contact any non earth being that had peace mind on my area,without thinking and positive result.

21 may 2016,almost 9.00 pm i try meditating but fail to gain focus,and i make a decision to sleep. wake up 1 am in the morning make a bottle of milk for my son(2 year old, my wife work at next town as teacher, so i am a father and mother) i feel more fresh and start meditating and do some random telepathy and  suddenly without any idea about thinking anything,i had a weak vision in my head to go "the place" that i know, not far away from my home (almost 1 hour drive)and very remote and the highiest point in my town (almost 650 meter form sea level, still puzzling about that weak vision, so i telepathy reply that vision "i agreed to meet at that place"and i dont recive any reply what!!

22 may 2016, i text my friend to come with me,but i dont tell him about the purpose of the meeting,i dont wanna be alone, that dangerous, just bring him to have some coffee at that "place" (small coffee shop & restaurant)at the top of that hill. i wait almost 3 hour but noting happen, so i decided to use telepathy (lol) to ask who was giving me vision to go here. suddenly face of the gray alien come in my head, no wonder why they not friendly to me. i was scare, my friend go to toilet and ask if we can back to town. i sad okey,im waiting you here, my friend walk to toilet area, and im start taking picture at the sky ( someone told me to do so) in my head. not telepathy (not a voice), just something ask me to do so. and i take 2-3 picture before leaving.

at that night a look back at the picture and i saw a silver orb one of the picture a take.

23 may 2016 at 5.30pm after i close my shop it was heavy rain and strong wind that day,i go in that place again alone i was very very scare, meditating in side my car, it was very dark and im alone, while i was meditating i hear weird sound i stop meditating the sound is gone, i back to meditate i hear the sound again (am i crazy) the sound like a electromagnet or something like that. noting happen i try take some picture but noting maybe it rain. so i go back home..

content.detailedDescription: I was inside watching tv when i noticed through one of a high window next to the fireplace a bright golden star in the south eastern direction. last week when i had seen it i went out onto my front porch to observe if it was a planet or a satellite . i started photographing it and when i zoomed in manual to get a better photo i noticed it was pulsating . so i began to video tape it. it then began to fade in and out several times. so tonight when i saw it again i went outside to watch to see if it was doing it again. when i noticed in the western sky there was a bright white starlight object. it also seemed to be pulsating a red green light. so i grabbed my new ipad and went out onto the front porch to try and get a better view. i manually zoomed in while video taping it and saw it was also a orb . it was also spinning . while video taping it . it started to move up out of my screens range. the last time i saw this white orb i took out my large telescope to look at it. i also made a report about it and should be on file. i have witnessed it before being stationary  and then traveling across the sky from east to west very quickly. faster than an airplane. this object can be seen from time to time in this area and i feel lucky to  experience this. i have also had company here that have witnessed these events and have seen it through the telescope also. it is a sphere that looks like it has a lot of lights or electrical lights running through it and is pulses  red and green . it also can bend itself to change its shape.  when it does happen to be here it stays for about three hours sometimes. being in a very rural area and city . people are in bed by dark and no one is out to look up an observe what is going on in our skies. it seems you can only see it on a very clear night.  the videos i have submitted are zoomed in . if you would like still photographs i can submit them also. the first video submitted is of tonight and the second one is of may 15 2016.  i would like your personal opinion on these.
content.summary: Bright stars that when seen through a telescope are  orbs in eastern tn skies. that pulse red and green lights and moves . it also fades in and out.

content.detailedDescription: I was in 8th grade coming home with 2 guys i play with but were not close friends with - i remember that it was 8th grade basketball practice which puts this event between october and december of 1976.  generally i was scared most of my life always looking down as i walked worried about what my father was going to do when i got home late.  i do not remember what the other 2 guys were doing but i remember that i found myself standing still looking at an angle of around 60 degrees through a tree -not a thick tree easy to see through it.  the ufo or should i say spaceship was directly above the tree which was around 50 ft tall.  i noticed that it had lights of the red variety moving around its perimeter.  i have no idea what was going on with the other 2 but i sensed they were in a trance like myself.  i felt that my mind was very slowly being engaged in some sort of thought exchange or maybe they were trying to ask me to do something( which is my surmise after 30 years of thinking about it) and i was getting more and more scared as time went by.  i actually remember now that in my mind i started playing this game where i was pretending to not understand what they were saying. i felt a sensitive loving communication not forcing or aggressive at all. then when i felt calmer i built up a little more courage and started really looking at it with more intent i tried to look into its windows for any activity and i might have seen something but not sure. i then said to myself ok they are about to leave hold my gaze on the ship so i can see where it goes and maybe even follow it -i know funny eventually it took off it went to the edge of my vision in about 1 second or less and veered off to the right with a red lighted trail.  all 3 of us snapped out of it and a police car was right there at that same moment the 2 guys went running to the cop car and started recanting the story and i ran home which happened to be 2 houses away  as i ran i heard the cop say yaa some people up the street said the same thing.  whatever went on with my communication it told me dont talk about this and besides my sister i told no one until about 20 or so years later it started coming up in conversation
content.summary: Me and 2 friends viewed a ufo above treetop hovering in a trance standing roughly 10 ft apart - i feel there was communication with my mind i was too scared to deal with could have been there 15 min or up to 30 it left quickly

content.altitude: 500 Feet or Less, Over 500 Feet (no cloudcover)
content.detailedDescription:
Watching tv out the window i noticed a black glass ball - it suddenly appeared in the field out my window.  the ball took off straight up like a fireball and looked like it was slingshot nw of the home. i ran  through the house out my garage and with my phone to video tape it when it there were two fireballs that were massive that kind of danced in a circle they were huge . my phone was not responsive - after turning it on and off - i got it to work. one of the orbs had disappeared and the other one suddenly got big and almost looked like there was a hollow center to it - then it became really small and began moving n- then my phone shut down instantly ... this is the only video of it i got  before my phone went black.

as i was trying to see what was wrong with my phone and typing this up - 3 helicopters are out in the sky over minot outskirts and surrey in the direction the orbs was when it began to get smaller and over our neighborhood. 

the black glass sphere - seemed to be at least 75ft in diameter.
content.summary: A black glass ball left a field on the east of home flew fast out to ne glowing orange

content.detailedDescription:
May 24th, approximately 10:25 pm est. 

i had walked out onto porch to smoke a cigarette before bed. while my fiance was inside getting our dog on the leash i stood on the porch smoking. i was looking up at the stars and saw what seemed to be one of the brightest stars in the sky kind of to the northeast moving easterly. as it went across the sky it seemed 3-4 times faster than a commercial jet but not nearly fast enough to be a shooting star. as it moved off to the east it just disappeared. the light turned off. there were no clouds in the sky, as i thought that might have been why i lost sight of it. it looked like a moving star. i was debating on whether or not to mention it to my fiance because i figured she would think i was crazy. i told her and as i was explaining that it could not have been a plane because it did not blink and was far too bright she saw the same thing. another star moving across the sky from west to east. they both held straight line flight paths and we're moving way faster than commercial jets we see but not as fast as shooting stars. i checked to make sure it wasn't  iss  or iridium flares. still not sure what to make of it.
content.summary: Two different star like objects moving in different directions

content.detailedDescription: My wife and i were canoeing on the susquehanna river between columbia and washington boro. on a sunday morning in august 16, 2015. the sky was slightly hazy and the air was fairly still. for no apparent reason i looked up and looked directly at a white/light gray sphere i estimated to be 3-5 feet diameter. this distance could be wrong i am not totally sure if i was looking at a small object close by or a large object far away. i concluded it must be small i could see the shading on the bottom as you would expect a solid round object to have. it looked like a volley ball just sitting there. it was not moving i did not want to take my eyes off of it or i would have trouble finding it against the same color sky. i pointed for my wife to look and she could not find it. after about 30 seconds it slowly faded away and i did not see it again.
content.summary: Gray/white dull sphere same color as the hazy sky in one spot about 300- 500 feet above me. slowly faded away.

content.detailedDescription:
This report was filled out at mufon headquarter from a letter received on may 24th, by field investigator l. flechtner.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

first report
on thursday may 10th, 1990, i was sitting in the front lawn staring at some very tall trees, suddenly, from low behind the trees on my left, an object appeared in the slightly over cast sky and zipped up and to the right at a 45 degree angle and disappeared behind the trees on the right. i saw a cylinder shaped, red/orange colored object over the treetops. it looked like glowing image of a fiery steel ingot. then soon afterwards, i saw a identical object do the same thing.

second report
on monday september 23, 1996, i was sitting in the back seat of a car, in front of a apartment building near athens. i saw a sphere of brilliant white light, below and to the right of the moon, traveling steadily at perhaps about five times the speed of a jetliner. it descended seemly into the ground. it was as big as an average two story house.And maybe a mile away. it was a couple thousand feet high when i first saw it.
content.summary: On thursday may 10th, 1990 i saw a cylinder shaped, red/orange colored object over the treetops

content.detailedDescription:
on sunday march 13th 2016, i thought i saw an airplane with a very bright red light coming towards me. then it stoped. i saw a  very bright red light, then it changed to a  very bright blue light, and then to a  very bright white light. it moved and repeated the sequence. then it moved and did the same thing again. then it left diagonally towards the reservoir. it seemed to have come from that area and went back to that area. shortly afterward i saw two different passenger airplanes go by. they had to have seen the lights too.
it was about helicopter high but i can't tell how faraway it was.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Straight-line path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: On sunday march 13th 2016, i thought i saw an airplane with a red light coming towards me. then it stoped. i saw a red very bright light, then it changed to a blue very bright light, and then to a white very bright light.

content.detailedDescription:
At 10pm uk time, i went into the garden at my home address to let my dog do his thing. out of the corner of my eye i noticed a glowing movement in the sky. i looked, expecting to see a commercial plane or such like and instead caught sight of approximately 3 fast moving objects with an orange flickering aura, which appeared to be launching from the north of essex. these were followed by 3 more almost immediately. they looked like fireworks being launched consecutively with approximately 2 second intervals in between, except they made almost no noise. the noise that i could hear though sounded like the very distant sound of and afterburner, that you might hear on a larger jet engine.
after about a 30-40 seconds of staring in disbelief, i ran to the back door and called to my grandfather to come and take a look. at this point i had all kinds of thoughts racing through my mind but i needed someone to confirm that i wasn't imaging this.
as he came out to take a look, 2-3 of the same objects had also taken to the skies, following exactly the same path as the first 6. all except the last one. it had a appeared to be moving in a more south-westerly direction and appeared to be launching later than the others, as well as being larger, slightly slower moving and with a more firey aura.
both my grandfather and i felt a little uneasy. i explained that i believed them to be missles and suggested why they might be in the sky. the only rational explanations i could think of was that we were under some kind of terrorist attack and these were being fired as some kind of deterrent or as an interception response to something very bad.
all of the objects appeared to just vanish at their highest point, and without any sign of an explosion or collision. i'm no expert but i summarised that if they were missles, it was as if they run out of fuel and missed their target.
i can't think what else they could have been. they travelled at a similar speed to what you might see a high altitude jet achieve.
after the event was over, i searched for some news about it on the web, hoping to find an explanation and when i found nothing, i searched for a way to report the event and found this website.
content.summary: 10pm uk time...I witnessed multiple glowing objects launch over essex and follow the same trajectory, except the last one. possibly missiles.

content.detailedDescription: I sat my camera on the ground to record the clouds this past sunday(5-22-16), and did not notice the object until later, while viewing the footage on my computer. in this clip, taken from the original video, the object is seen about 18 seconds in. it seems to waver just a tiny tiny wee bit as it passes above the cat shaped cloud.
content.summary: Small dot moving swiftly across sky

content.detailedDescription:
on monday the 23rd of may, at about 6 am, i was taking out the trash when i saw a triangle craft hovering over my neighbors house across the street. it was lower than the power lines. it had pulsating lights around the edges. they were purple, orange and red. it had a large red light in the center of the bottom. the craft was black and had some hieroglyphics in gray on the side of the craft. it made no noise. i watched it for a while and then it shot straight up into the air. my house faces the southwest. the neighbors were not home at the time. dogs were barking in the neighborhood until the craft left. 
the weather was partly cloudy and raining in some areas, but not raining at the time i saw the craft. when it shot up into the sky it made a hole in the cloud.
content.summary: Monday the 23rd of may at about 6 am i was taking out the trash when i saw a triangle craft hovering over my neighbors house across the street
